com.gwtplatform.dispatch.client

Class RpcDispatchAsync

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.gwtplatform.dispatch.client.AbstractDispatchAsync
      • com.gwtplatform.dispatch.client.RpcDispatchAsync
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DispatchAsync
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DefaultDispatchAsync, PhoneGapDispatchAsync

    public class RpcDispatchAsync
extends AbstractDispatchAsync
    This class is the default implementation of DispatchAsync, which is essentially the client-side access to the Dispatch class on the server-side.
